  "title": "Rs. 695 bn Supplementary Budget receives cabinet nod",
  "body_lines": [
    "The proposal to submit a supplementary\u00a0estimate for the provision of Rs. 695 billion under the \u2018Budget Assistance Services and Emergency Responsibilities\u2019\u00a0project of the National Budget\u00a0Department\u00a0received the Cabinet nod on Monday.",
    "The proposal has put forward by Premier Ranil Wickremesinghe in his capacity as\u00a0Minister of Finance, Economic Stabilization, and National Policies.",
    "According to the\u00a0Department of Government, it has been decided\u00a0to submit a supplementary estimate to Parliament to cover the cost and secure the necessary funds to maintain the essential public services without hindrance."
  ],
